org.jobscheduler.dashboard.config

Class WebConfigurer.NoAnalyticsAtmosphereFramework

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.atmosphere.cpr.AtmosphereFramework
      • org.jobscheduler.dashboard.config.WebConfigurer.NoAnalyticsAtmosphereFramework
  • Enclosing class:
    WebConfigurer

    public class WebConfigurer.NoAnalyticsAtmosphereFramework
extends org.atmosphere.cpr.AtmosphereFramework
    Atmosphere sends tracking data to Google Analytics, which is a potential security issue.

    If you want to send this data, please use directly the AtmosphereFramework class.
